snippet: Police have concluded that Ariel Castro, who pleaded guilty to imprisoning three women in Cleveland for a decade, committed suicide by hanging in his cell.
abstract: Ohio police conclude that Ariel Castro, who pleaded guilty to imprisoning three Cleveland women for a decade, committed suicide by hanging in his prison cell.
